# ============================================================
# NOTES
# ============================================================

# 1. Most ocean data APIs (NOAA, NASA, USGS) are FREE for educational/research use
# 2. Always respect API rate limits to avoid being blocked
# 3. Store real keys in .env.local (NOT committed to git)
# 4. For production, use environment variables in Azure App Service
# 5. Firebase anonymous auth is COPPA compliant (no personal data collection)
# 6. Keep VAPID private key secure - never commit to repository
